Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">&nbsp;AI 领域的顶尖研究者和技术领袖，全球最牛逼的 AI 科学家之一。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100044267\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20390580&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruxJbLcVUPJCDsiaZ0MVUY9k49CCrYdic8dr77fuMMBrKlHBeMNpFZAt1WPUOx7L8Y8nf5lKF8Wic4YZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mgud89wd1ruh\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">OpenAI 的创始成员</span>，在 2015-2017 &nbsp;年参与深度学习、生成模型和强化学习工作，推动了 GPT 模型的早期探索，并协助公司搭建技术团队。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;li